title: O'Neill x Parley for the Oceans
description: O’Neill, the legendary surf company founded in 1952 by Jack O’Neill in Santa Cruz, California, proudly announces their partnership with Parley for the Oceans, an organization dedicated to raising awareness as to the fragile state of our oceans and turning the tide on ocean plastic and ocean destruction.
